    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5607315/" class="title-link">我爱你</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5607315"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/wagobian/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u57331024-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wagobian/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">我改变</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-10-06"
      class="main-meta">2012-10-06 00:17:38</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5607315_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                        花花绿绿的世界，不知什么时候，让人变的很不安很浮躁。焦虑、犹豫、怨恨、嫉妒接踵而来，除了痛苦，生活还是一成不变。偶尔会有一种揪心的痛，累，从心底而生。        你改变不了世界，你能改变的只有你自己，你的感官意识和别人没有关系，哪些都是你自己创造的。     ...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5607315_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5607315_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










